---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Concepts & Ascents and the writer behind it."
>
  <article class="about">
    <h1 class="essay-title">About</h1>

    <hr class="essay-rule" />

    <div class="essay-body">
      <p>
        <em>Concepts &amp; Ascents</em> is a venue for short essays at the intersection
        of metaphysics, philosophy of religion, and the contemplative traditions.
        The questions taken up here are old: the structure of reality, the relation
        of unity to multiplicity, the soul's ascent to the One, and the long conversation
        between Greek philosophy and the revealed traditions that drew it forward.
      </p>

      <p>
        It is written by <strong>Rashad Abdulsalam</strong>, who reads in the
        Neoplatonic and Akbarian lineages — Plotinus, Ibn ʿArabī,
        al‑Ghazālī, and their contemporary interpreters. He is based in
        Florida.
      </p>

      <p>
        The aim is modest: to organize a body of thought slowly, in public, and
        in writing that is precise rather than ornamented.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <p class="contact">
        Correspondence is welcome at <a href="mailto:hello@conceptsandascents.com"
          >hello@conceptsandascents.com</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about .contact {
    text-indent: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
